 426:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Parameters
 427:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    pRing        Ring buffer to post to.
 428:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    pBuffer      Pointer to character array. Does not need to point to a \0 terminated string.
 429:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    NumBytes     Number of bytes to be stored in the SEGGER RTT control block.
