 553:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Function description
 554:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Reads characters from SEGGER real-time-terminal control block
 555:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    which have been previously stored by the application.
 556:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Do not lock against interrupts and multiple access.
 557:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Used to do the same operation that J-Link does, to transfer 
 558:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    RTT data via other channels, such as TCP/IP or UART.
 559:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *
 560:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Parameters
 561:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    BufferIndex  Index of Up-buffer to be used.
 562:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    pBuffer      Pointer to buffer provided by target application, to copy characters from RTT-up-
ARM GAS  C:\Users\Administrator\AppData\Local\Temp\ccUGyMKj.s 			page 23


 563:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    BufferSize   Size of the target application buffer.
 564:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *
 565:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Return value
 566:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    Number of bytes that have been read.
 567:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *
 568:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *  Additional information
 569:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** *    This function must not be called when J-Link might also do RTT.
 570:Middlewares/Third_Party/SEGGER/RTT/SEGGER_RTT.c **** */
